        self.phone_numbers = [PhoneNumber(**p) for p in phone_numbers] if isinstance(phone_numbers[0], dict) else phone_numbers

class PhoneType(object):
   MOBILE = 0
   HOME = 1
   WORK = 2

class PhoneNumber(object):
    
    def __init__(self, number=None, type=PhoneType.HOME):
        self.number = number
        self.type = type

class AddressBook(object):

    def __init__(self, people=[]):
        self.people = [Person(**p) for p in people] if isinstance(people[0], dict) else people
        
    # getters and setters omitted
